      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, u said i should keep an eye on bleeding... is it really okay to mix them? i thought mixing blood thinners with things like ibuprofen was dangerous. i don't want to end up in the hospital, but the headache is getting really intense. should i just go ahead and take 400mg of ibuprofen now?",
